She raised an eyebrow at Plintissa. She was going to build her own base.. and form her own group? Ha! What a joke! How many people did sh think were going to join apart from herself and Dracona? 

"Your own group? And Base? Where are you going to get all the equipment? Surely you are not going to steal it.. are you?"

If Plintissa was going to steal from the Maximals, or anyone else for that matter.. she didn't think she was going to like her! But she let the bot say her answer first..
